"***Question 1: \"How likely is it that Bond will escape from Le Chiffre?\"***\n5. Moderately likely\nBond has already shown a willingness to fight back and has attempted an escape, indicating resourcefulness and a fighting spirit. However, he is currently overpowered and disarmed, which tempers the likelihood of immediate success.\n\n***Question 2: \"How suspenseful do you find this passage to be?\"***\n6. Very suspenseful\nThe passage is filled with action, as Bond makes a daring attempt to escape and protect Vesper, only to be swiftly and skillfully thwarted. The tension is heightened by the immediate danger Bond faces and the uncertainty of his next move or the consequences of his failed attempt."